# Optional for local development: copy to ".env" in this folder (next to app.py).
# The Streamlit dashboard uses OpenSky + ADSBDB (no airline API key).
#
# On Streamlit Cloud, world-wide /states/all is huge; the app uses regional boxes first.
# For better rate limits, register an API client at https://opensky-network.org/ and set:
#   OPENSKY_CLIENT_ID=...        (client id, e.g. user@example.com-api-client)
#   OPENSKY_CLIENT_SECRET=...     (secret from the portal — never commit this file with real values)
# Or in Cloud: Settings → Secrets → same keys (TOML: [ ] section with key = "value").
# Without these, the app still calls OpenSky anonymously.
